    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The old man sought, as Lot had done, to defend his guests from such a shameful crime by appealing to the sacred rights of hospitality, and by giving up his own virgin daughter and the concubine of his guest (see the remarks on ",
